<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include ('common/Nav');%>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <div class="card shadow">
            <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white text-center">
              <h3>About Us</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <p>
                Welcome to our project management platform! We aim to provide a simple and effective
                solution for tracking issues and bugs in your projects.
              </p>

              <h5>Our Mission</h5>
              <p>
                To streamline project management by offering a user-friendly interface for creating,
                managing, and tracking project issues.
              </p>

              <h5>Features</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Build a neat UI</li>
                <li>Show a list of projects on the home page</li>
                <li>Allow users to create a new project</li>
                <li>Project Detail Page to show bugs related to the project</li>
                <li>Filter issues by labels, author, and search by title and description</li>
                <li>Create a new issue for a project</li>
              </ul>

              <h5>Issue Tracker</h5>
              <p>
                Our platform includes an issue tracker inspired by popular solutions like Github.
                You can manage your project's issues efficiently with features such as filtering,
                searching, and creating new issues.
              </p>

              <h5>Get Started</h5>
              <p>
                Explore our platform, create projects, track issues, and enhance your project
                management experience. We look forward to supporting your development journey!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include ('common/Footer'); %>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
